## Push workflow

After committing changes, push to both GitHub and the local backup:

```bash
npm run push
```

This pushes to:
- **origin** (GitHub): `https://github.com/jburton321/ONE-AGENCY-WEBSITE.git`
- **local** (Desktop backup): `~/Desktop/ONE-AGENCY-WEBSITE`

Or manually:
```bash
git push origin main
git push local main
```
